lead_paragraph: Barcelona's Luis Suarez netted twice for a 2-1 win over 10-man Atletico Madrid in their Champions League quarter-final, first leg on Tuesday after the visitors' Fernando Torres opened the scoring and was later sent off.

headline.print_headline: Suarez Double Sees Barca Recover to Beat 10-Man Atletico
